dc_description_s: Relief shown by 5 feet contour interval and spot heights. Map shows provincial, district, planning area, municipal or township, property and cadastral boundaries. "Crown copyright reserved." "All sheet numbers are prefixed 64/3. Thus: - 64/3/9SW4." "The representation on this map of a road, track or footpath is no evidence of a right of way."
